vdsn" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-59wgfr" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Rcvb2:"><div data-rid="169514b5-5129-40e0-bf92-5a075e7a05dd" class="r-gfz0m2"><div data-rid="9a61740f-3383-4fc7-a43b-952a0b74154b" class="r-117u2ld alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Arccos Smart Laser is accurate to within ±1 yard.</p><p><br></p><p>The laser delivers precise line-of-sight distance, then layers in slope, wind speed, wind gusts, wind direction, temperature, and humidity to calculate a true "Plays Like" number. So you're not just getting an accurate yardage — you're getting the right yardage for the conditions in front of you.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="57c02486-556c-447c-a21d-a273c095585a" class="r-5eg2m8" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="11cf68e4-11c2-4548-9bb9-eb6ed6010cc5" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rkvb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-fddyla"><div data-rid="27735b70-e3b7-4e26-8525-8e16a3269153" class="r-fot45g alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Do I need an Arccos game-tracking membership to use the Smart Laser?</p></span></div><div data-rid="35cce262-19f4-4e2b-9957-6fb5552d7c9d" class="r-17vbbic" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1tqnn16" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Rkvb2:"><div data-rid="ad486097-3d4b-44ff-bb2e-2e91bef65352" class="r-sos3i1"><div data-rid="cd507c45-dd03-4a16-baeb-6929f1a8fe6f" class="r-7dszu0 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>No. The Smart Laser is a standalone product and works independently.</p><p>You can add game tracking later, but it’s not required.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="c225eaf6-79ea-46f3-917d-e8feadae50bc" class="r-15mjx45" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="38fd503f-cf95-4051-8cc8-09530e4ed265" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rsvb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-x9nlat"><div data-rid="b279965a-6e55-405b-8c28-0377b9ef9f4e" class="r-1fsr2lf alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>What happens if I lose or break my Smart Laser?</p></span></div><div data-rid="5f4d4167-605f-4949-9b05-add772a8375c" class="r-ynq3j5" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-b9otch" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Rsvb2:"><div data-rid="ec4d3482-9507-46fc-a563-610101642fd5" class="r-4jj2c6"><div data-rid="a8e1db65-3734-4cfe-8399-323723abc2c8" class="r-4bxjar alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>If your device is lost or damaged, you’ll be able to purchase a replacement for a one-time fee. Your subscription remains active and tied to your account.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="eade6fcc-6db3-4d08-a49c-45121eabcfb5" class="r-jb4ru2" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="ebb2bf51-9dff-41a6-aebe-c88eaa410e35" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R14vb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1c2x7vv"><div data-rid="e430128e-f326-4607-bd4f-e31931f6abd1" class="r-1hxfuuv alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>How is this different from a regular rangefinder with slope?</p></span></div><div data-rid="9c4ffc00-3976-4980-8784-666c09ea6b52" class="r-cmylvp" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1qw7bwd" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R14vb2:"><div data-rid="02500047-e227-4ae2-b963-9068e31c131e" class="r-e15owi"><div data-rid="49ef2e37-959d-4347-a886-7a670b9f74fb" class="r-oh8qyi alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Most rangefinders stop at slope. Arccos Smart Laser goes further — adjusting for wind speed, wind gusts, wind direction, temperature, and humidity on top of slope to calculate a true "Plays Like" distance. You're not just getting a line-of-sight number. You're getting the right number for the conditions you're actually playing in.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="9e772cbe-cf8c-479e-996d-fc4e51d82251" class="r-40seag" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="b6b3c24c-f17f-4532-b35d-acb519575ce5" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R1cvb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-la4bj7"><div data-rid="330fc157-22ea-4d10-8dc7-3459a57495ec" class="r-mex3k alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Is this legal for tournament play?</p></span></div><div data-rid="f5ee46c3-45ad-4d85-9aa5-4d6d2e6318b2" class="r-kro09x" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-nrknau" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R1cvb2:"><div data-rid="600fff10-abe3-40b6-b937-8897ce4f1488" class="r-adrd44"><div data-rid="9fa5f564-09dd-4a4b-9c97-b7eae6f5789e" class="r-t1219z alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Yes — when tournament mode is enabled.</p><p>The Smart Laser includes a conforming mode that disables slope and environmental adjustments to meet competition rules.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="b7c9425c-4bc3-46eb-a1eb-69a5f926a58e" class="r-43ismk" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="6d8ea8f5-d3e2-4d58-9fad-6c191b8e79c4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R1kvb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1wxb0vp"><div data-rid="fe662f73-33d8-4fa3-a1b1-54e902acd9e5" class="r-1suc82t alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Do pros actually use this?</p></span></div><div data-rid="160a9020-33c3-4cf4-b4e2-687a51553f46" class="r-1xtpnhq" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1d72z20" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R1kvb2:"><div data-rid="fe052565-c256-4b97-96d6-4a9840a8be76" class="r-1ih7yqz"><div data-rid="c76f94b2-3092-4ed2-ad3e-11042a156352" class="r-zpnis3 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Yes. Major Champion Matt Fitzpatrick uses the Arccos Smart Laser and game-tracking data to dial in strategy and yardages. Tour players trust precision — and that's exactly what this delivers.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="fd6a0985-1500-4820-ba25-31acf23a2ed8" class="r-1xnpxtu" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="9203e953-4e96-4b2f-8d8c-7574ebb30645" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R1svb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1j1a487"><div data-rid="5d16808e-1ec7-498a-a46b-a887cc185f8d" class="r-16huzg8 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Why does the Smart Laser require a subscription?</p></span></div><div data-rid="cafe04be-484b-468f-ac36-c013feee689b" class="r-1dugwl7" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1nx79f" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R1svb2:"><div data-rid="936fc451-c555-4915-b83e-d4457a475a6b" class="r-1odhi9t"><div data-rid="f85cdb43-dc41-436f-b59b-0d4e383f929a" data-ullist-text="" class="r-opvg9e alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Unlike standard rangefinders, the Smart Laser runs on continuously evolving software, so it keeps getting better after you buy it.</p><p>Your subscription keeps your device updated with:</p><ul><li><p>AI strategy recommendations</p></li><li><p>Green Maps (where available)</p></li><li><p>Live weather adjustments</p></li><li><p>Ongoing software improvements</p></li></ul><p>It's not just hardware — it's a platform that improves over time.</p></span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="575bf585-31c4-4b1c-8a97-d9ffb39d9d9c" class="r-1rtfzhv"><picture data-rid="05b3ec78-47e3-4a87-b0e4-3f253692445a" class="r-1dilc48"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/824a366a-dafd-4375-8504-aacc62618158/8e2e3f88-bbec-4f3d-b499-5879d0343609?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/824a366a-dafd-4375-8504-aacc62618158/8e2e3f88-bbec-4f3d-b499-5879d0343609?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/824a366a-dafd-4375-8504-aacc62618158/8e2e3f88-bbec-4f3d-b499-5879d0343609?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/824a366a-dafd-4375-8504-aacc62618158/8e2e3f88-bbec-4f3d-b499-5879d0343609" class="r-8v1mlv" loading="lazy"/></picture></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>
